de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.datageneration.dependency
Interface Dependency

All Known Implementing Classes:
DependencyImpl
public interface Dependency

To generate proper test data it may be important to know the dependencies of attributes. This interface tries to fill the gap. If any dependency exists between attributes it's important to compute the attribute to which another attribute depends.

In test data generation view, a dependency means, an attribute uses the results of another attribute. That attribute could itself depend on any other attribute or attributes.
